      <h1 class='title'>Fuel Poverty</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1667WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1667ws' title='Col. 1667WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1667WS' name='column_1667ws' href='#column_1667ws' rel='bookmark'>1667WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_93'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-chris-ruane' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_93' title='Link to this speech by Mr Chris Ruane' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-chris-ruane" title="Mr Chris Ruane">Chris Ruane</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs how much public money was spent in insulating and improving heating in<span class="italic">(a)</span> elderly and<span class="italic">(b)</span> low income homes in each of the last 25 years. [186107]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_94'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-elliot-morley' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_94' title='Link to this speech by Mr Elliot Morley' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-elliot-morley" title="Mr Elliot Morley">Mr. Morley</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">Since the establishment of Defra in June 2001, the Warm Front scheme, which provides a range of insulation and heating measures to private households in England, has spent approximately &#x00A3;296.6 million. Of this, around &#x00A3;220 million has been spent on the elderly.</p><p>The Energy Saving Trust, which is grant funded by my Department, also provides support to local authorities to run local energy efficiency programmes.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
